This paper discusses the Web of Linked Data, which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves the use of semantic web technologies. The paper also discusses the development stack and scripting languages, which are topics related to software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the consumption and processing of data, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and deep learning (cs.DL).
